<br>
::He hobbled over to his table and sat down, and poured himself a glass of wine. He sat silently and drank, letting thoughts run through his head. Within his forge, while he worked he seemed to forget the world...even himself. Now everything was cathing up to him. He finished the glass of wine and looked into the forge::<br>
<br>
::He saw some of the cyclopes hard at work. He sighed and spoke out:: &quot;I shall return eventually...I need a break.&quot;<br>
<br>
::The cyclopes looked up for a moment, smiled to him and then continued their work:: <br>
<br>
::Hephaestus grabbed his walking crutch and disappeared in a cloud of soot and smoke. Not a few moments later, he appeared on the beach of the island of Lemnos. Ever since his father, Zeus, had thrown him off Olympus and he landed her, after trying to stop a fight between Zeus and Hera, this place had become somewhat special to him. The residents had nursed him back to health, and he in turn took a certain liking to them.::<br>
<br>
::He looked around and disrobed his clothing. After working the forge for as long as he has, he had developed quite a build. He wasn't quite as well chiseled as perhaps some of the other Olympians, but he equalled, if not surpassed, quite a few of them in strength. He looked down at his lame leg and shook his head. He immediatly headed into the ocean for a swim. He was pretty average looking, which by Olympian standards could be considered ugly, but it was his bum leg that truley made him horrid in the eyes of the Olympians. He waded in the ocean, trying to forget all of his worries::<br>
<br>
::As he was swimming around on the shore, he started chanting a rhyme he learned when he was young:<br>
<br>
&quot;Nobody loves me, everybody hates me;<br>
Guess I'll go eat worms,<br>
Big fat juicy ones<br>
Little itty bitty skinny ones<br>
Guess I'll go eat worms!&quot;<br>
<br>
::He shook his head and laughed to himself::<br>
<br>
::Mutters under his breath:: &quot;Boy, oh, boy did I hate my childhood.&quot; <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ixhephaestusxi>IX Hephaestus XI</A> at: 4/8/03 11:06:24 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ixhephaestusxi>IX Hephaestus XI</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 32<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(4/8/03 10:57 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=308.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Work-a-holic</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://elfwood.lysator.liu.se/loth/v/a/vasilis/hephaestus.jpg.html"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--> <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ixhephaestusxi>IX Hephaestus XI</A> at: 4/8/03 11:06:51 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=persephoneqofu>PersephoneQofU</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 171<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(4/8/03 4:18 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=308.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.aishwarya-rai.com/tradi/tash16.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> A Nice Hello</span><hr size=1> ::Persephone appears on the beach in a soft little lawn chair with a shade and with a glass of ambrosia wine in her hand. Oberving Hephaestus, she smiles openly admiring his built physique, from head to toe.. Persephone had seen her share of less than average looking people down in the Underworld. So Hephaestus being plain looking never struck her as a hideous thing.::<br>
